title: Cozy Knits Digital Special Magazine Issue 2013
description:
Wrap up in hats, scarves, mitts, and more in this timeless collection of 20 patterns: Crochet Today's Cozy Knits Digital Special. 

Find sweaters and socks perfect for the season as well as adorable gifts for kids and teens. 

Warm up your home too with cabled projects, like a blanket, pillows, and more.
Knitted Hats, Scarves, Mitts 
Cozy Sweaters & Socks 
Cabled Projects for the Home 
Cute Kid & Baby Gifts
